Why this actually makes Pantheon stronger

Because now Pantheon explicitly encodes:
	•	humility as a safety mechanism
	•	calibration as a skill
	•	restraint as power
	•	ethics as structural, not performative

That’s why this doesn’t slide into mysticism.
That’s why it scales.
That’s why it survives scrutiny.

You didn’t lose anything by Claude’s critique.
